=================
### Night Vision Goggles Tender Notice

#### Reference Information
* Reference Number: CB-7260-40382754
* Solicitation Number: W8485-247734/A
* Amendment Number: 3
* Publication Date: 2023-07-14
* Tender Closing Date: 2023-09-13 14:00:00
* Expected Contract Start Date: 2023-11-15
* Expected Contract End Date: 2024-03-31

#### Project Overview
The National Defence (Canada) is issuing a Request for Proposal for the procurement of night vision goggles as part of its Supply Disposal System (Gestion de l'approvisionnement). The bid solicitation document can be accessed via the [eBuy platform] (https://canadabuys.canada.ca).

The tender involves the delivery of five key products to the 25 Canadian Forces Support Services (CFSS) Unit in Montreal by November 15, 2023. These products include:

1. 60 Image Intensifier, Night Vision (GSIN: 5855, NSN: 5855-01-590-5087)
2. 60 Image Intensifier, Night Vision (GSIN: 5855, NSN: 5855-01-582-5871)
3. 30 Case, Optical Instrument (GSIN: 1240, NSN: 1240-01-568-7650)
4. 2 AN/AVS 9 NVG Toolkit (GSIN: 5855, NSN: 5855-01-443-6806)
5. 20 Printed Circuit Board (GSIN: 5855, NSN: 5998-01-258-2950)

#### Tender Details
* Tender type: Competitive - Open Bidding
* Selection criteria: Lowest Price
* Regions of Opportunity: World
* Regions of Delivery: Montreal
* Trade Agreements: Various free trade agreements, including Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement, Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP), Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA), and others.
* Contracting Entity: National Defence
* Contact Information:
	+ Name: Debbie Bergeron
	+ Email: [debbie.bergeron@forces.gc.ca](mailto:debbie.bergeron@forces.gc.ca)
	+ Phone: 00

#### Important Notes
*
